\frac{x_1+x_2}{2} \geq \sqrt{x_1x_2} \quad x_1,x_2 \geq 0</script><p>它的证明很简单</p>
<script type="math/tex; mode=display">
(\sqrt{x_1}-\sqrt{x_2})^2 \geq 0 \\
\Leftrightarrow x_1^2+x_2^2-2\sqrt{x_1x_2} \geq 0 \\
\Leftrightarrow \frac{x_1+x_2}{2} \geq \sqrt{x_1x_2}</script><p>证毕</p>]]>
